   <title>Posting (nothing) is easy</title>
   <link href="droidekas.github.io/site/posting-nothing-is-easy.html"/>
   <updated>2015-01-22T00:00:00+05:30</updated>
   <id>droidekas.github.io/site/posting-nothing-is-easy</id>
   <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Starting a site is actually quite easy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npmjs.com/package/generator-jekyllized&quot;&gt;generator&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install everything to run the generator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix a few &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/rowoot/gulp-gh-pages/issues/13&quot;&gt;bugs&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And then serve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Voila!&lt;/u&gt;
&amp;lt;!&amp;ndash;more&amp;ndash;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maintaining a website?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.Well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.Well&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.&lt;strong&gt;Well&amp;hellip;&amp;hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Its even harder when you really don’t know what to blog about.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I like experimenting, and this site is essentially going to be my play ground. A lot of thought even went into choosing this platform and framework. Hopefully it shall pay off.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the meantime, to compensate for the incapability of blogging, I shall just give a running commentary on how this website morphs. Maybe if I figure how to change website states so that the current state reflects the post? Let’s see.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
